{"tid":2245500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台行政院蘇貞昌質疑陳同佳「渣男不如」 促港府與台灣司法互助把陳送台受審","createTime":"2020-10-16T09:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T10:03:39.000Z","uid":241764,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"764e0342c215faf5ae945b28fd6d7183f1e49f53","tid":2245500,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"在台灣涉嫌殺害女友潘曉穎的港男陳同佳，出獄後近一年來多次宣稱要赴台自首但遲遲未有起行，長期協助陳的牧師管浩鳴前天（14日）曾現身香港的台北經濟文化辦事處，疑欲為陳申辦赴台簽證，但據報已被台灣當局拒絕批出簽證，引起各界關注。台灣行政院長蘇貞昌今日受訪時批評，陳同佳不只是渣男，只講「渣男」太客氣，因陳是殺人犯。故蘇促請港府與台灣司法互助，並希望被害者父母要求香港特區政府協助將陳繩之以法。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201016/THZG6GLYQ5ANRDXEAVVCNYC3DY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3KiY8ujeuvapBap8OVeoU4LzSnmCh0kL7VGnUP4He0wZors1hm4hFGmig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201016%2FTHZG6GLYQ5ANRDXEAVVCNYC3DY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3KiY8ujeuvapBap8OVeoU4LzSnmCh0kL7VGnUP4He0wZors1hm4hFGmig&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=8c19de41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201016%2FTHZG6GLYQ5ANRDXEAVVCNYC3DY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3KiY8ujeuvapBap8OVeoU4LzSnmCh0kL7VGnUP4He0wZors1hm4hFGmig&h=d5bd70cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201016/THZG6GLYQ5ANRDXEAVVCNYC3DY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3KiY8ujeuvapBap8OVeoU4LzSnmCh0kL7VGnUP4He0wZors1hm4hFGmig</a>"},{"pid":"b898aef7c852c3f4c8a3a13ea9d4865cd601e7dc","tid":2245500,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":